FiveEqualsFiveStillCoerces
/ Regression anchor: a number 5 still equals the text "5" — cross-kind equality coercion was
/ not lost when scalars became born-native. The comparison coerces and the branch runs.
- set %a% = 5
- set %b% = "5"
- set %matched% = false
- if %a% equals %b%
    - set %matched% = true
- assert %matched% is true
